Ufakazi ozifihlile owaziwa ngoMr X, oqale ukufakaza ngoMsombuluko, umnikazi wenkampani yokwakha eseRichards Bay, uthe wathintwa yi-project manager yaseMhlathuze uMnuz Mboniseni Majola, wathi ufuna ukufaka imali enkampanini yakhe. Uthe ekuqaleni wayenokungabaza kodwa wagcina evumile. Uthe lokhu kukokotela kwakwenzeka kanjena, kwakuba nezinkampani ezahlukene zonjiniyela ezazithola umsebenzi eMhlathuze Water, bese zona zithumela imali kwi-akhawunti yenkampani yakhe. Uma izinkampani zonjiniyela sezikhokhele yena bese esetshela uMajola. “UMajola wanginikeza ipheshana elinezinombolo zasebhange okumele ngidlulisele khona le mali. Ngangilinda yena ukuba angitshele ukuthi ngenzenjani ngemali,” kusho uMr X. Ikhomishini iyaqhubeka. 